            <title><![CDATA[With Australian Games Media On Its Knees, A New Magazine Is Trying To Keep A Scene Alive]]></title>
            <link>https://aftermath.site/australian-video-game-magazine-continue/</link>
            <guid>1459243</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div id="main">
      
    <div data-post-hero="fullwidth-image">

    <div data-post-hero-content="">
          

      

        <p>'We'll be chasing stories from across the planet'</p>

        
    </div>

